333
00:20:58,523 --> 00:21:00,525
All this celebrating.

334
00:21:00,525 --> 00:21:03,027
You should see the place.

335
00:21:03,028 --> 00:21:04,529
Bloody ruined.

336
00:21:04,529 --> 00:21:05,530
