No, thank you.

423
00:25:15,280 --> 00:25:17,282
I'm trying
to cut down.

424
00:25:17,282 --> 00:25:18,783
Good.

425
00:25:18,783 --> 00:25:21,285
You don't seem
to need alcohol

426
