as well?

441
00:26:46,871 --> 00:26:48,873
No, she's clean.

442
00:26:48,873 --> 00:26:50,374
Rich tourist.

443
00:26:50,375 --> 00:26:51,376
Not a political bone

444
00:26:51,376 --> 00:26:53,878
