since he got here.

452
00:27:08,393 --> 00:27:09,894
Yeah, but now
the South Africans

453
00:27:09,894 --> 00:27:10,895
are showing an interest.

454
00:27:10,895 --> 00:27:11,896
Oh, really?

455
00:27:11,896 --> 00:27:13,898
