from Pretoria.

456
00:27:13,898 --> 00:27:16,400
[Sighs]
Here, look.

457
00:27:16,401 --> 00:27:17,902
See him?

458
00:27:17,902 --> 00:27:21,405
<i>Sitting at the bar?</i>

459
00:27:21,406 --> 00:27:22,407
<i>He's not local.</i>

460
00:27:22,407 --> 00:27:25,410
<i>He's got tribal scars</i>
<i>and an accent.</i>

461
00:27:25,410 --> 00:27:28,413
<i>The South African consul here</i>
<i>moonlights for their service.</i>

462
00:27:28,413 --> 00:27:31,416
