to avoid the issue?

478
00:28:22,467 --> 00:28:24,469
Well...

479
00:28:24,469 --> 00:28:25,970
Well what?

480
00:28:25,970 --> 00:28:27,972
Diana.

481
00:28:27,972 --> 00:28:28,973
You're a gorgeous girl.

482
00:28:28,973 --> 00:28:30,975
