himself.

494
00:29:08,012 --> 00:29:11,015
Campo alegre at 10:00
on Thursday evening.

495
00:29:11,015 --> 00:29:12,016
If you agree.

496
00:29:12,016 --> 00:29:15,019
Forget it.

497
00:29:15,019 --> 00:29:19,023
This is a very
important person, Stephen.

498
00:29:19,023 --> 00:29:20,524
